title: YouTube usage penetration in the United States 2019 , by age group
summary: The chart at hand is a line chart where the x axis denotes Year and a y axis denotes Reach. In total the number of data points it has is 5.
In general Reach has fallen over the Year.
Reach is slightly decreasing from 15-25_years to 26-35_years, roughly constant from 26-35_years to 46-55_years, and lastly slightly decreasing from 46-55_years to 56+_years.
The steepest decrease occurs in between the Year 15-25_years and 26-35_years.
Maximum Reach, about 81.0 was reported at Year 15-25_years
Minimum Reach about 58.0 was reached at Year 56+_years
